description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Cocker Spaniel puppy hugging a kitten
-Squirrel and Wren
-Rabbit and Cat
-Seagull crosses the sea on pig's back
-Cat, dog and ducklings
-Rabbit and goat kid
-Cat and Duckling
-Butterfly on frog's head
-Rabbit and Chick
-Golden Retriever and Horse
name: The Magical Bond Between Animals
